com.slickpath.mobile.android.simple.vm.instructions

Interface Instructions

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseInstructionSet, VirtualMachine

    public interface Instructions
    Contains the string and integer definitions for all the instructions

    If command value is 0 - 999 : No Parameters 1000 - 1999 : 1 Parameters All other values : Undefined

    Author:
    Pete Procopio
